{"tid":1763920,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"要整hardisk 求救","createTime":"2019-11-30T17:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T17:27:19.000Z","uid":271593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"decb3e6f4fd97bcbd8c9308534a29ff80a2f2123","tid":1763920,"uid":271593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"話說小弟有個external hardisk 入面有好多之前去旅行既相(好不幸地冇留曬底係其他地方)<br />\n有一日插入電腦之後就話要format左先可以用 就知道又出事<br />\n後尾知道可以用chkdsk.exe 呢個function啦 點知就話空間不足做唔到repair<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請教下連登巴絲可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我知係出面整會好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想知有冇D平D方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7e6f7bc7a0fdc2c5bb8fbee7f6f7c324cc44ac","tid":1763920,"uid":92340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"唔好用chkdsk，分分鐘咩都冇<br />\n其實啲資仲係到<br />\ngoogle hard disk recovery tool<br />\nrecuva之類"},{"pid":"05a1b431a2a131d72bc5281594c2242896da64a0","tid":1763920,"uid":113115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:13:52.000Z","msg":"iCloud  google photos 會唔會有"},{"pid":"8b90a738b364a11ff6d3fa9dfc10ead60ed98c38","tid":1763920,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:27:19.000Z","msg":"chkdsk係垃圾, 如果你隻碟真係有故障, 你chkdsk有機會衰多兩錢重<br />\n軟件上, 反正都係要全碟scan, 直接搵啲recovery tool睇下scan到幾多出嚟好過<br />\n硬件上, 如果係舊款既, 可以試下拆出嚟, 有機會係就咁轉接, 可以就咁隊SATA<br />\n唔得就俾錢人搞啦<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n(好